如果你想减肥,你明白的

62
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:01,000
If you change your diet, you exercise.
如果你改变饮食,你运动。

63
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:03,000
The weight will come off, or at least we hope so.
重量会下降,至少我们希望如此。

64
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:10,000
Now, those things that framework gives the world a sense of coherence.
现在,那些框架赋予世界一种一致性感的东西。

65
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:15,000
Second big idea associated with meaningfulness in life, second big idea.
第二个大点子 与生活中的有意义有关,第二个大点子。

