它给了你目标。

72
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:36,000
When you get up in the morning, you know what you need to do.
当你早上起床时 你知道你需要做什么

73
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:40,000
Here's where the drive for personal achievement is strongest.
这是个人成就最强劲的动力

74
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,000
It's clearest.
这是最清楚的。

75
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:45,000
When I was worried about 10 year-end, you were exactly what I need to do when I got up in the morning.
当我担心十岁大的时候 你正是我早上起床时 需要做的

76
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:52,000
